name: mou frio
description:
it's cold in curitiba (my city), like the currently brazilians hearts. this first piece is part of me and it's to introduce main my style: colorful elves, my beats and of course a bit (or a lot) of politics. #ForaBolsonaro 

this beat was made in the 271th session of Beat Brasilis, a pioneer Brasil's beatmakers meeting, which during the pandemic is being online.

illustration, animation and soundtrack by @numadessas at HIC ET NUNC
